Subject: [PATCH] RDMA/qedr: Fix kernel panic when trying to access recv_cq
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.11.14
Git-commit: e1ad897b9c738d5550be6762bf3a6ef1672259a4

[ Upstream commit e1ad897b9c738d5550be6762bf3a6ef1672259a4 ]

